description: Stunning Penthouse with 2 private outdoor decks and central air!  Lovely West side home that features an open floor plan between a kitchen w/ excellent cabinet space and living room with over 9 ft ceilings overlooking your first back deck.  Walk up a private staircase to your roof deck space with city views and cool breeze. The home also boasts a modern bathroom, great closet space, private storage and just about the biggest bedroom you will ever find in this price range perfect to designate office space. Beyond its remarkable interior, this home is part of a strong condo association, boasting substantial reserves and recent upgrades including a new roof, siding, and decks. With proximity to the beach, public transportation, vibrant nightlife, delectable eateries, and downtown Boston, this property is not only a dream home for an owner, but also a savvy investment opportunity. Showings begin Friday and through the weekend.  Offers if any, will be reviewed Monday at 5pm on 5/20.
